Configure DNS
Map test.example.com to the Ingress Controllerâ€™s EXTERNAL-IP:

If you are using Route 53, create an A record pointing test.example.com to the Load Balancer's EXTERNAL-IP.
Alternatively, update your local /etc/hosts file for testing:
======================
<EXTERNAL-IP> test.example.com
Test the setup by accessing:

=============================
http://test.example.com
You should see:
Hello from NGINX Ingress!
